f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b845188c2921134282b58a41d30b108e943fb455","tid":528833,"uid":50988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"發現咗人大承諾就好唔可信"},{"pid":"886f0ac2488a6d9dcdf372baf383c5c89475afc4","tid":528833,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"因為人都係善變的"},{"pid":"93a7c2d667badc31d82aab7cf74c1f6382798301","tid":528833,"uid":43130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"所以無論對住邊個都唔好下巴輕輕"},{"pid":"865c049ccf61e4a3c292d579aeb09492e03407fb","tid":528833,"uid":143307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係大個咗就明白<br />\n人係會變<br />\n每一分每一秒都變緊<br />\n<br />\n承諾當下可能係真心<br />\n但真心敵不過時間"},{"pid":"cb0016645254d392f6476213b120ef7ba4491a21","tid":528833,"uid":2373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"甚麼承諾都只是謊言，人到最後只會為自己著想，嘥鳩氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2caeb0db9c4b45f3e8e52c9221a5b38cecee367f","tid":528833,"uid":105344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:39:05.000Z","msg":"好心淡 好想信人 但唔敢再信"},{"pid":"6407fd682fe6a929681819e9e0890d5ff3cabcde","tid":528833,"uid":1952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:19:47.000Z","msg":"分咗手之後 諗返起啲承諾就好心痛<br />\n之後有機會拍拖都唔會再信<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPromise me no promises <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934853c1810e5d191cab61a3cc352cff6c0a6dfa","tid":528833,"uid":106203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6407fd682fe6a929681819e9e0890d5ff3cabcde","tid":528833,"uid":1952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:19:47.000Z","msg":"分咗手之後 諗返起啲承諾就好心痛<br />\n之後有機會拍拖都唔會再信<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPromise me no promises <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"散左一個月一諗返起岩岩一齊啲承諾。<br />\n真係心諗，男人要追你個陣真係咩撚都講得出。<br />\n完全冇諗過佢黎手就掉個下係幾傷人。<br />\n利申藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a21da8b60c127261fc64930e63d4cd4b1da583","tid":528833,"uid":71389,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"分咗手唔通又繼續兌現承諾咩<br />\n承諾喺分開嗰刻已經唔存在兌現力<br />\n<br />\n我話過會佢生日後求婚<br />\n分開咗幾年我亦照求<br />\n只會被人覺痴漢而非痴情<br />\n<br />\n利申 最後有求"},{"pid":"a9de46f82d8b2ca28aecaa1971ac4edca2b756f3","tid":528833,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分咗手唔通又繼續兌現承諾咩<br />\n承諾喺分開嗰刻已經唔存在兌現力<br />\n<br />\n我話過會佢生日後求婚<br />\n分開咗幾年我亦照求<br />\n只會被人覺痴漢而非痴情<br />\n<br />\n利申 最後有求</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身覺得巴打好犀利好清醒<br />\n見到最後一句<br />\n好心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08930b441375098627cf19933fe5048b794f3d3a","tid":528833,"uid":74281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"係你自己笨撚柒姐 怪咩人 死傻仔"},{"pid":"02d0df8e07ab5be0df1f413aa16ddda350d8cf66","tid":528833,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:16:01.000Z","msg":"要走的總要離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f